

This is a standalone code.

To compile it : 

1- Configure  :

TRIQS_PATH=/path/to/installed/triqs/base   cmake /path/to/triqs_source/triqs/examples/ising1d/

e.g. :  TRIQS_PATH=/home/parcolle/BUILD/TRIQS_epd_free/INSTALL_DIR/ cmake /home/parcolle/triqs_source/triqs/examples/ising1d/

2- Compile
make

3- Set : 

 * PYTHONHOME if you did not compile with the system python, e.g. 
   export PYTHONHOME=/usr/local/EPD/

 * of course, 
   export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/path/to/installed/triqs/base/lib

4- Run :  e.g.

LABO:~/BUILD/Ising $ ./ising1d 
Ising 1D

